# Security Style

- Do not log PII from library code.
- Fail closed on misconfig (e.g., backend='redis' without redis_url) with clear exceptions.
- Namespace keys to avoid cross-env collisions.
- Avoid broad `except:`; raise typed library exceptions or rethrow after logging.
